Siku moja, Biantaka alimwendea jirani yake kumuomba chungu kikubwa ili akitumie kuchota maji. Jirani yake alikubali kumwazima Biantaka chungu kikubwa. Alisema, "Tatizo la jirani yangu ni tatizo langu."
